title: CUSTOM KALISTA PC CASE

embed.description: The Internet's visual storytelling community. Explore, share, and discuss the best visual stories the Internet has to offer.

body:
Hi guys, Last week I posted my corsair carbide air240 twisted fate pc case and had a good reaction,
that was my prototype, here is my new Bloodmoon Kalista design with my gamer tag on the backside of my pc.
Let me know what you guys think

replies.body:
I like it, but I preferred the TF one. I think his splash was just more appropriate for this.
Anyway though, you're doing good work. It'd be cool to see if you do anything else in the future.
could you do a braum or poro one? :3

Didn't you just do one for TF :D

Nice job anyway.
